body:
@lukecwik any clue on the error here?

It is the Spark runner `WordCountIT` run, which should include the dependencies to have `TestSparkPipelineOptions` where `--forceStreaming` is defined. Clearly the initial options parse worked, but then when it was turned back into args and then re-parsed in `WordCount.main` the parser does not know about the spark options.

I will be unavailable for the rest of today, so anyone should feel free to clone this PR if it is helpful for fixing the postcommit.
